remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-102">智慧標籤已啟用時，圖表會重新定位重疊的資料點標籤，根據一組使用者定義的規則。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-102">When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-103">註標線會繪製連結包含其資料點標籤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-103">Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-104">您可以控制在註標線的視覺屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-104">The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-105">這些視覺屬性包含色彩、 線條樣式與線條寬度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-105">These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>屬性控制的裝飾，如箭頭，並出現在註標線結尾。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-107"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A>屬性可以設定為任何<xref:System.Drawing.Color>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-108">如果您設定的註標線的色彩，您將也會自動設定的色彩<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>和定義所裝飾<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-108">If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-109"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A>屬性會控制在註標線的像素寬度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-110">使用此屬性也會調整的裝飾<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-110">Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-111">可以透過使用數個影片相關屬性控制的智慧型標籤移動。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-111">The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-112">這些定義的規則的移動方向，距離與標籤的資料點是否可保留在繪圖區。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-112">These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-113">預設移動規則通常會解決大部分問題。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-113">The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-114"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>定義指定的最大距離，單位為像素的資料點，允許資料點標籤重疊時可移動的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-115"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>屬性會定義指定的最小距離，單位為像素的資料點重疊時，會移動資料點標籤的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-115">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-116">當資料點標籤需求，可以重新定位時，標籤將會移動至少指定像素數目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-116">When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-117"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>屬性會指出無法解決重疊問題時，是否隱藏標籤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-117">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-118">如果<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>屬性是`true`，而且無法繪製資料點，所指定的區域內<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>所允許之方向<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>，不會繪製資料點標籤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-119"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>屬性會定義可以在其中移動資料點標籤 direction(s)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-119">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-120">這個屬性會接受一個<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>值或位元 OR 多個<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-120">This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8717-121">預設值是位元 OR 所有<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>值，以允許所有可能的方向不同的資料中心點中重新定位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-121">The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8717-122">下列圖表類型不支援智慧型標籤：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-122">Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a8717-123">橫條圖： 橫條和 100%堆疊橫條圖。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-123">Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a8717-124">形狀： 圓形圖、 環圈圖、 極座標圖和雷達圖。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-124">Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a8717-125">範圍圖表： 範圍、 範圍的資料行和範圍橫條圖。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-125">Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="a8717-126">堆疊區域圖： 堆疊區域和 100%堆疊區域圖。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8717-126">Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
  
   ' Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.Enabled = true  
  
   ' Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined  
  
   ' Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   ' Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash  
  
   ' Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3   
  
   ' Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
{  
   // Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined;  
  
   // Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   // Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash;  
  
   // Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3;  
  
   // Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow;  
}  
```
